      "text": [
        " : \"لاَ يَشْتَرِي مِنْ أَرَاضِي أَهْلِ اَلسَّوَادِ شَيْئاً إِلاَّ مَنْ كَانَتْ لَهُ ذِمَّةٌ فَإِنَّمَا هِيَ فَيْءٌ لِلْمُسْلِمِينَ \"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3879 - It is narrated from Abu Al-Rabi' Al-Shami, from Abu Abdillah (as), who said:\n\"Do not purchase anything from the lands of the Sawad except from those who have a covenant, for it is a spoils (fay') for the Muslims.\""
        ]
      }
